text: Catskill may refer to the following in the U.S. state of New York: * Catskill (town), New York, in Greene County ** Catskill (village), New York, in the above town * Catskill Creek, a tributary of the Hudson River * Catskill Mountains ** Catskill Park, a protected area in the Catskill Mountains * Bark mill, also known as Catskill's mill
title: Catskill
